# 💭 InnerVoice - Anonymous Confession Wall

InnerVoice is a beautifully designed, interactive and safe space for users to anonymously express their thoughts and feelings. Built using PHP, MySQL, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

---

## 🌸 Features

- 🔐 Anonymous posting (no login required)
- 🌼 Aesthetic confession wall with pastel theme
- 📝 Live confession posting with JavaScript
- 🔥 Abusive language detection and validation
- 💖 Emoji reactions and reply support (coming soon)
- 📌 Confession tracking using localStorage

---

